<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ArteLu | Academia de Deportes Aéreos</title>

    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            darkMode: 'class',
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        primary: "#52054d",
                        secondary: "#2f328a",
                        accent: "#bca0dd",
                        highlight: "#ab5b9f",
                        lightbg: "#efefdc",
                        neutralgray: "#d9d9d9",
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>


    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css" />

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css" />

    <link rel="icon" href="/assets/logo.png" type="Logo de ArteLu" />
</head>

<body
    class="flex flex-col min-h-screen bg-lightbg text-primary dark:bg-gray-900 dark:text-neutralgray transition-colors duration-500">

    <%- include('./partials/navbar.ejs') %>

        <main class="flex-1">
            <section id="inicio" class="relative h-screen overflow-hidden">


                <div id="slider" class="absolute inset-0 flex transition-transform duration-700 ease-in-out">
                    <% for(let i=1; i <=10; i++) { %>
                        <div class="min-w-full h-screen bg-cover bg-center"
                            style="background-image: url('/assets/hero<%= i %>.png')">
                        </div>
                        <% } %>
                </div>

                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50"></div>

                <div class="relative h-full flex items-center justify-center text-center px-6">
                    <div class="text-white max-w-3xl">
                        <img src="/assets/Letras.png" alt="Letras ArteLu" class="mx-auto mb-2 w-48 md:w-96">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-6">
                            Academia de Deportes Aéreos
                        </h2>
                        <p class="mb-8 text-lg md:text-xl">
                            Fuerza • Arte • Movimiento • Libertad
                        </p>

                    </div>
                </div>


                <button id="prevSlide" class="absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-20 text-white text-3xl">
                    ❮
                </button>

                <button id="nextSlide" class="absolute right-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-20 text-white text-3xl">
                    ❯
                </button>


                <div id="dots" class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-20 flex gap-2">
                </div>

            </section>

            <section id="nosotros"
                class="py-16 md:py-28 px-6 bg-[url('/assets/fondo2.png')] bg-no-repeat bg-opacity-50 bg-center">
                <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold font-style: italic mb-10 font-mono">
                    Nosotros
                </h3>
                <div
                    class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-justify md:text-left">
                    <p class="text-2xl font-style: italic font-bold">
                        Somos el resultado de una idea principal: Si algo te apasiona,
                        hazlo en serio.
                    </p>
                    <br>
                    <p>
                        Tras varios años de trabajo, decidimos crear un grupo de enseñanza con la intención de ser la
                        mas grande academia de artes aéreas de Venezuela.
                    </p>
                    <br>
                    <p>
                        Nuestro principal cometido es difundir, promover y fomentar las Artes Acrobáticas en el país, su
                        estudio de manera integral y su aplicación profesional como medio de vida.
                    </p>
                    <br>
                    <p>
                        Somos un gran equipo, con varios años de experiencia y desempeñando con mucha libertad creativa
                        nuestro campo de desarrollo. En ArteLu somos fieles a una filosofía de trabajo única, formulada
                        para el
                        máximo desempeño y crecimiento.
                    </p>
                    <br>
                    <p>
                        Todos son bienvenidos a conocer este arte y acercarte a las actividades de este grupo aéreo.
                    </p>
                    <br>
                    <p>
                        Te brindamos toda la información necesaria para que tomes la iniciativa de acompañarnos en este
                        proceso de creación y crecimiento compartiendo nuestra actividad.
                        Deseamos que sea de tu agrado.
                    </p>
                    <br>
                    <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex justify-center">
                        ATREVETE A VOLAR CON NOSOTROS!
                    </h4>
                </div>

                <div class="flex justify-center items-center py-10">
                    <a href="/teamArteLu" class="bg-highlight hover:bg-secondary dark:bg-accent text-white dark:text-black text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold 
              px-10 py-5 rounded-full shadow-lg transform transition-all 
              duration-300 hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-2xl inline-block text-center">
                        Conoce a nuestro equipo
                    </a>
                </div>
            </section>

            <script>
                window.datosClases = <%- JSON.stringify(disciplinas || []) %>
            </script>

            <section id="clases" class="bg-neutralgray dark:bg-gray-800 py-28 px-6">
                <div class="">
                    <h3 class="text-5xl font-extrabold font-style: italic mb-10 font-mono text-primary dark:text-white">
                        Clases
                    </h3>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-6">

                        <% if (disciplinas && disciplinas.length> 0) { %>
                            <% disciplinas.forEach(d=> { %>
                                <% if (d.activa) { %>
                                    <div onclick="abrirModalClase('<%= d._id %>')"
                                        class="group relative flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-dark shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all border border-neutral/20 dark:border-white/5 cursor-pointer">

                                        <div class="aspect-square w-full bg-neutral/20 relative overflow-hidden">
                                            <div class="aspect-square w-full bg-neutral/20 relative overflow-hidden">
                                                <% const principal=d.imagenes && d.imagenes.length> 0
                                                    ? (d.imagenes.find(img => img.esPrincipal) || d.imagenes[0]).url
                                                    : null;

                                                    const nombreLimpio = d.nombre.replace(/\s+/g, '+');
                                                    const fotoFinal = principal ||
                                                    `https://placehold.co/600x400/52054d/white?text=${nombreLimpio}`;
                                                    %>

                                                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110"
                                                        style="background-image: url('<%= fotoFinal %>');">
                                                    </div>

                                                    <div
                                                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent opacity-60">
                                                    </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div
                                                class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent opacity-60">
                                            </div>
                                        </div>

                                        <div class="p-3 flex-1 flex flex-col justify-between bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
                                            <div>
                                                <span
                                                    class="text-secondary dark:text-white inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] font-bold bg-accent/20 mb-1">
                                                    PARA TODOS
                                                </span>
                                                <h4
                                                    class="text-secondary dark:text-white font-bold text-base leading-tight mt-2 uppercase">
                                                    <%= d.nombre %>
                                                </h4>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="mt-2 flex items-center justify-between">
                                                <span
                                                    class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 font-semibold group-hover:text-highlight transition-colors">
                                                    Ver detalles <i class="fa-solid fa-plus ml-1"></i>
                                                </span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <% } %>
                                        <% }) %>
                                            <% } else { %>
                                                <div class="col-span-3 text-center py-10">
                                                    <p class="text-xl text-gray-500">Pronto publicaremos nuestras
                                                        clases.</p>
                                                </div>
                                                <% } %>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="actividades" class="py-28 px-6">
                <h3 class="text-5xl font-extrabold font-style: italic mb-10 font-mono">Actividades</h3>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">


                    <div
                        class="group relative flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-dark shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all border border-neutral/20 dark:border-white/5">
                        <div class="aspect-square w-full bg-neutral/20 relative overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110"
                                style="background-image:url('https://placehold.co/60x40');">
                            </div>
                            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent opacity-60">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-3 flex-1 flex flex-col justify-between">
                            <div>
                                <span
                                    class="text-secondary dark:text-white inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] font-bold bg-accent/20 text-secondary mb-1">
                                    3 PARTICIPANTES
                                </span>
                                <h4 class="text-secondary dark:text-white font-bold text-base leading-tight">
                                    COMPETENCIA
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mt-2 flex items-center justify-between">
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">1er Lugar</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>



                    <div
                        class="group relative flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-dark shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all border border-neutral/20 dark:border-white/5">
                        <div class="aspect-square w-full bg-neutral/20 relative overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110"
                                style="background-image:url('https://placehold.co/60x40');">
                            </div>
                            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent opacity-60">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-3 flex-1 flex flex-col justify-between">
                            <div>
                                <span
                                    class="text-secondary dark:text-white inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] font-bold bg-accent/20 mb-1">
                                    3 PARTICIPANTES
                                </span>
                                <h4 class="text-secondary dark:text-white font-bold text-base leading-tight">
                                    COMPETENCIA
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mt-2 flex items-center justify-between">
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">1er Lugar</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="group relative flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-dark shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all border border-neutral/20 dark:border-white/5">
                        <div class="aspect-square w-full bg-neutral/20 relative overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110"
                                style="background-image:url('https://placehold.co/60x40');">
                            </div>
                            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent opacity-60">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-3 flex-1 flex flex-col justify-between">
                            <div>
                                <span
                                    class="text-secondary dark:text-white inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] font-bold bg-accent/20 text-secondary mb-1">
                                    3 PARTICIPANTES
                                </span>
                                <h4 class="text-secondary dark:text-white font-bold text-base leading-tight">
                                    COMPETENCIA
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mt-2 flex items-center justify-between">
                                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">1er Lugar</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>



                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Elfsight AI Chatbot | Untitled AI Chatbot -->
            <script src="https://elfsightcdn.com/platform.js" async></script>
            <div class="elfsight-app-fba2c842-93e3-4d91-be23-45234b1815aa" data-elfsight-app-lazy></div>

            <button id="openModal"
                class="fixed bottom-20 right-16 md:bottom-28 md:right-6 bg-highlight hover:bg-secondary dark:bg-accent text-white dark:text-black transition px-4 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-semibold">
                Reserva tu Clase Ahora
            </button>
            <%- include('./partials/modal-clase.ejs') %>
                <%- include('./partials/aside.ejs') %>
                    <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>

        </main>

        <script type="module" src="/js/inicio.js"></script>
        <script type="module" src="/js/aside.js"></script>

</body>

</html>